trans:
You should speak
softly to get ready.

Do you have
a cough drop?

text:
カラオケで
歌いすぎたりしたか
trans:
Did you sing too
much during karaoke?

name: 愛依
text:
サンキュ！　別に調子は悪くないんだけどさ
ちょっと出が不安だったんだよね～
trans:
Thank you! My throat's not actually
sore, I'm just a little nervous~

name: 愛依
text:
ん～、調子は悪くないから大丈夫っぽいけど
ま、一応もらっとくわ！
trans:
Yeah, I'm fine since my throat isn't that bad.
Well, I'll take one just in case!

name: プロデューサー
trans:
(It seems she got some
peace of mind from that)

name: 愛依
text: いやいや、さすがにうちもそこまではやんないよ？
trans:
Not at all, wouldn't you expect me
to stop before that happened?

name: プロデューサー
text: （悪い勘繰りをしてしまった）
